# We Offsite — Warm Editorial Luxury

## Skill activo
`high-end-visual-design` — arquetipo Editorial Luxury (crema, serif, grain, full-bleed)

## JERARQUÍA
1. Este archivo + tokens en `global.css` → fuente de verdad visual
2. `design-system/we-offsite/MASTER.md` → desactualizado, pendiente sync
3. `.agents/skills/` → referencia anti-slop solamente

## PALETA
- Canvas: `#FDFBF7` | Surface: `#FFFFFF` | Espresso: `#1C1410`
- Muted: `#787774` | Rust CTA: `#C4522A` | Gold focus: `#C9A962` | Sage labels: `#6B7F6E`

## TIPOGRAFÍA
- Display: Playfair Display | Body: DM Sans | Labels/stats: Space Mono
- NO Inter, Lexend, Geist, Satoshi

## MOTION (MOTION_INTENSITY: 5)
- CSS + Intersection Observer únicamente
- NO GSAP, NO Framer Motion
- prefers-reduced-motion: solo opacity

## COMPONENTES
- Cards: double-bezel (`rounded-2xl` outer, inner calc radius)
- Buttons: nested pill CTA rust + icon circle
- Nav: floating island pill
- Case studies: layout editorial asimétrico + glare hover

## PRE-FLIGHT
- Lucide SVG, cursor-pointer, 4.5:1 contrast, focus gold 2px
- loading/empty/error states, min-h-[100dvh], responsive 375/768/1024/1440
